                            <comment id="18009057" author="tilman" created="Tue, 22 Jul 2025 17:55:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reading this file with PDFDebugger gets me an EOF. The segment from PfbParser.java that you want to change isn&apos;t in the code. (Maybe it is in another change?)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One could argue that the existing code isn&apos;t secure enough&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; size = in.read();
size += in.read() &amp;lt;&amp;lt; 8;
size += in.read() &amp;lt;&amp;lt; 16;
size += in.read() &amp;lt;&amp;lt; 24;
LOG.debug(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;record type: {}, segment size: {}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, recordType, size);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] ar = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[size];
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;that &quot;size&quot; should be checked against the length of the input.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
